HEADWORD: overstated
<hw>overstated</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>represented as greater than is
true or reasonable; exaggerated; <as>as, They made <ex>overstated</ex>
accusations of corruption</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> exaggerated, overdone.</syn>⟦br⟧
